Brief Russian psychological dictionary: 1. A super-pessimist is a person who does not turn on the alarm clock for tomorrow morning.2. A pessimist is a person who refrains from buying a monthly pass.3. A realist is a man planting tomato seedlings in March. 4. An optimist is a person who buys new skis in March.5. A super-optimist is a person who issues a new passport.